# mkisofs

> Create ISO files from directories
> Also aliased as `genisoimage`
> More information: https://manned.org/mkisofs

- Create an ISO from a directory:

`mkisofs -o {file value: sample.iso} {directory value: source}`

- Set the disc label when creating an ISO:

`mkisofs -o {file value: sample.iso} -V "{string value: label_name}" {directory value: source}`
